  - id: BETH_R2
    speaker: Ally Quinn
    line: "Morning of the 14th, they came in looking wrecked. Asked Beth if
      she knew anyone who could help a person start over somewhere new. Beth
      thought they were joking. I don't think they were."
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 792b5f88f6dd2724d84b6954cc0b5fad,
